                                      font-weight="bold">元</text>
                            </g>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h1 class="intro-title">公元一九四九</h1>
                    <div class="intro-divider">
                        <span class="deco-line left"></span>
                        <span class="deco-dot">◆</span>
                        <span class="deco-line right"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="intro-text" id="intro-text">
                        <p>1949年春，汕头德兴路86号。</p>
                        <p>一位名叫林希之的年轻化学家，正为打破欧美感光技术垄断而日夜奋战。</p>
                        <p>他缺钱、缺设备、缺人手……但他坚信：<span class="emphasis">"中国必须有自己的感光材料！"</span></p>
                        <p>今天，你穿越时空，成为了他的助手。</p>
                        <p>请完成一系列使命，见证中国感光工业从零到一的奇迹——</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="intro-signature">
                        <span class="signature-text">汕头工业博物馆</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button id="start-btn" class="stamp-btn">
                    <span class="stamp-text">开始闯关</span>
                    <span class="stamp-border"></span>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="ink-splash ink-1"></div>
            <div class="ink-splash ink-2"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- 板块总览页 -->
        <div id="overview-page" class="page">
            <div class="overview-container">
                <div class="overview-header">
                    <h2>汕头工业博物馆</h2>
                    <h3>公元感光工业探秘</h3>
                    <p>穿越时空，成为林希之的助手<br>见证中国感光工业从零到一的奇迹</p>
                </div>
                <div class="overview-sections">
                    <div class="overview-card section-1-card" data-section="1">
                        <div class="overview-card-icon">🔥</div>
                        <div class="overview-card-info">
                            <h4>第一板块</h4>
                            <h3>光辉起点 · 工业摇篮</h3>
                            <p>📍 第一馆·历史展厅（1层）</p>
                            <div class="overview-card-badges">
                                <span>🚶</span><span>💡</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="overview-card-status">
                                <span class="status-text">2枚徽章</span>
                                <span class="status-dot"></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="overview-card-arrow">→</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="overview-card section-2-card locked" data-section="2">
                        <div class="overview-card-icon">🔧</div>
                        <div class="overview-card-info">
                            <h4>第二板块</h4>
                            <h3>匠心传承 · 技艺追踪</h3>
                            <p>📍 第一馆·历史展厅（1-2层）</p>
                            <div class="overview-card-badges">
                                <span>🥇</span><span>🏭</span><span>🧪</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="overview-card-status">
                                <span class="status-text">3枚徽章</span>
                                <span class="status-dot locked">🔒</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="overview-card-arrow">→</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="overview-card section-3-card locked" data-section="3">
                        <div class="overview-card-icon">⚙️</div>
                        <div class="overview-card-info">
                            <h4>第三板块</h4>
                            <h3>智慧工厂 · 挑战闯关</h3>
                            <p>📍 第二馆（设备展区）</p>
                            <div class="overview-card-badges">
                                <span>🧩</span><span>⚗️</span><span>⚡</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="overview-card-status">
                                <span class="status-text">3枚徽章</span>
                                <span class="status-dot locked">🔒</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="overview-card-arrow">→</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="overview-footer">
                    <p>集齐全部8枚徽章，解锁专属荣誉证书！</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ink-splash ink-1"></div>
            <div class="ink-splash ink-2"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- 主游戏页面 -->
        <div id="game-page" class="page">
            <header class="game-header">
                <div class="header-title" id="section-title">光辉起点 · 工业摇篮</div>
                <div class="badge-progress">
                    <span class="badge-icon">🏅</span>
                    <span id="badge-count">0</span>/8
                </div>
            </header>

            <main class="game-content">
                <!-- 板块一 -->
                <section id="section-1" class="section active">
                    <div class="section-banner banner-1">
                        <div class="banner-overlay">
                            <h2>第一板块</h2>
                            <h3>光辉起点 · 工业摇篮</h3>
                            <p>📍 第一馆·历史展厅（1层）</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="level-list">
                        <div class="level-card" data-level="1">
                            <div class="level-num">01</div>
                            <div class="level-info">
                                <h4>重走创业路</h4>
                                <p>寻找林希之的实验室</p>
                                <span class="level-tag">拍照打卡</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="level-status">
                                <span class="status-icon locked">🔒</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="level-card" data-level="2">
                            <div class="level-num">02</div>
                            <div class="level-info">
                                <h4>科研微光</h4>
                                <p>76次试验的坚持</p>
                                <span class="level-tag">知识问答</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="level-status">
                                <span class="status-icon locked">🔒</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section-reward">
                        <div class="section-sparks" id="sparks-1"></div>
                        <div class="reward-badge" id="reward-badge-1">
                            <span class="reward-icon">🔥</span>
                            <span class="reward-name">公元星火</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="reward-desc">集齐2枚徽章解锁</p>
                        <div class="section-level-badges" style="margin-top:10px; display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:10px;">
                            <span style="font-size:1.5rem; opacity:0.3;" id="s1-badge-1">🚶</span>
                            <span style="font-size:1.5rem; opacity:0.3;" id="s1-badge-2">💡</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- 板块二 -->
                <section id="section-2" class="section locked-section">
                    <div class="section-banner banner-2">
                        <div class="banner-overlay">
                            <h2>第二板块</h2>
                            <h3>匠心传承 · 技艺追踪</h3>
                            <p>📍 第一馆·历史展厅（1-2层）</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="section-lock">🔒 需完成板块一</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="level-list">
                        <div class="level-card locked" data-level="3">
                            <div class="level-num">03</div>
                            <div class="level-info">
                                <h4>寻找第一</h4>
                                <p>找寻三件珍贵展品</p>
                                <span class="level-tag">展品打卡</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="level-status">
                                <span class="status-icon locked">🔒</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="level-card locked" data-level="4">
                            <div class="level-num">04</div>
                            <div class="level-info">
                                <h4>厂房印记</h4>
                                <p>厂址变迁的故事</p>
                                <span class="level-tag">匹配游戏</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="level-status">
                                <span class="status-icon locked">🔒</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="level-card locked" data-level="5">
                            <div class="level-num">05</div>
                            <div class="level-info">
                                <h4>原料大收集</h4>
                                <p>胶片原料知多少</p>
                                <span class="level-tag">打地鼠</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="level-status">
                                <span class="status-icon locked">🔒</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section-reward">
                        <div class="section-sparks" id="sparks-2"></div>
                        <div class="reward-badge" id="reward-badge-2">
                            <span class="reward-icon">🔧</span>
                            <span class="reward-name">匠心探客</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="reward-desc">集齐3枚徽章解锁</p>
                        <div class="section-level-badges" style="margin-top:10px; display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:10px;">
                            <span style="font-size:1.5rem; opacity:0.3;" id="s2-badge-1">🥇</span>
                            <span style="font-size:1.5rem; opacity:0.3;" id="s2-badge-2">🏭</span>
                            <span style="font-size:1.5rem; opacity:0.3;" id="s2-badge-3">🧪</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- 板块三 -->
                <section id="section-3" class="section locked-section">
                    <div class="section-banner banner-3">
                        <div class="banner-overlay">
                            <h2>第三板块</h2>
                            <h3>智慧工厂 · 挑战闯关</h3>
                            <p>📍 第二馆（设备展区）</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="section-lock">🔒 需完成板块二</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="level-list">
                        <div class="level-card locked" data-level="6">
                            <div class="level-num">06</div>
                            <div class="level-info">
                                <h4>拼图大师</h4>
                                <p>复原老厂区照片</p>
                                <span class="level-tag">拼图游戏</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="level-status">
                                <span class="status-icon locked">🔒</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="level-card locked" data-level="7">
                            <div class="level-num">07</div>
                            <div class="level-info">
                                <h4>化学魔法师</h4>
                                <p>感光化学的奥秘</p>
                                <span class="level-tag">连线配对</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="level-status">
                                <span class="status-icon locked">🔒</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="level-card locked" data-level="8">
                            <div class="level-num">08</div>
                            <div class="level-info">
                                <h4>效率大师</h4>
                                <p>设备进化七十年</p>
                                <span class="level-tag">排序游戏</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="level-status">
                                <span class="status-icon locked">🔒</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section-reward">
                        <div class="section-sparks" id="sparks-3"></div>
                        <div class="reward-badge" id="reward-badge-3">
                            <span class="reward-icon">⚙️</span>
                            <span class="reward-name">工业达人</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="reward-desc">集齐3枚徽章解锁</p>
                        <div class="section-level-badges" style="margin-top:10px; display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:10px;">
                            <span style="font-size:1.5rem; opacity:0.3;" id="s3-badge-1">🧩</span>
                            <span style="font-size:1.5rem; opacity:0.3;" id="s3-badge-2">⚗️</span>
                            <span style="font-size:1.5rem; opacity:0.3;" id="s3-badge-3">⚡</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </main>

            <!-- 底部导航 -->
            <nav class="bottom-nav">
                <div class="nav-item active" data-section="1">
                    <span class="nav-icon">🔥</span>
                    <span class="nav-text">板块一</span>
                </div>
                <div class="nav-item locked" data-section="2">
                    <span class="nav-icon">🔧</span>
                    <span class="nav-text">板块二</span>
                </div>
                <div class="nav-item locked" data-section="3">
                    <span class="nav-icon">⚙️</span>
                    <span class="nav-text">板块三</span>
                </div>
                <div class="nav-item" id="nav-certificate">
                    <span class="nav-icon">📜</span>
                    <span class="nav-text">证书</span>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </div>

        <!-- 关卡弹窗容器 -->
        <div id="level-modal" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content" id="modal-content">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 徽章获得弹窗 -->
        <div id="badge-modal" class="modal badge-modal">
            <div class="badge-modal-content">
                <div class="badge-glow"></div>
                <div class="badge-big" id="badge-big-icon">🏅</div>
                <h3 class="badge-modal-title">获得称号</h3>
                <p class="badge-modal-name" id="badge-modal-name">重走创业路</p>
                <div class="badge-modal-fragment" id="badge-modal-fragment">
                    <span class="fragment-icon" id="badge-fragment-icon">🔬</span>
                    <span class="fragment-label">收集到</span>
                    <span class="fragment-name" id="badge-fragment-name">实验室碎片</span>
                </div>
                <button class="stamp-btn small" id="badge-modal-close">
                    <span class="stamp-text" id="badge-modal-btn-text">继续探索</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 彩蛋弹窗 -->
        <div id="easter-modal" class="modal easter-modal">
            <div class="easter-content">
                <div class="easter-stars">✨</div>
                <h3 id="easter-title">隐藏彩蛋！</h3>
                <p id="easter-desc">你触发了一个惊喜！</p>
                <button class="stamp-btn small" id="easter-close">
                    <span class="stamp-text">太棒了</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 日记弹窗 -->
        <div id="diary-modal" class="modal diary-modal">
            <div class="diary-content">
                <div class="diary-header">
                    <span class="diary-icon">📖</span>
                    <h3>林希之日记</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="diary-date" id="diary-date">1949年6月2日 · 深夜</div>
                <div class="diary-body">
                    <p id="diary-content">今晚，中国第一张原始氯素照相纸诞生了！虽然只是薄薄一片，但它承载的，是整个民族的希望。</p>
                    <p class="diary-signature" id="diary-author">—— 林希之</p>
                </div>
                <div class="diary-actions">
                    <button class="diary-btn" id="diary-play">
                        <span>🔊</span> 朗读日记
                    </button>
                    <button class="stamp-btn small" id="diary-close">
                        <span class="stamp-text">继续探索</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 最终彩蛋弹窗 -->
        <div id="final-easter-modal" class="modal final-easter-modal">
            <div class="final-easter-content">
                <div class="final-easter-glow"></div>
                <div class="final-easter-icon">🔍</div>
                <h3 id="final-easter-title">林希之的秘密</h3>
                <p id="final-easter-desc">所有板块都完成了！但林希之还有一个秘密，藏在这座博物馆的角落里。</p>
                <div class="final-easter-clue">
                    <span class="clue-label">💡 线索</span>
                    <p id="final-easter-clue-text">博物馆出口附近公元厂年表展板，在楼梯拐角处。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="final-easter-actions">
                    <button class="final-easter-btn" id="final-easter-found">
                        ✅ 我找到了
                    </button>
                    <button class="stamp-btn small" id="final-easter-close">
                        <span class="stamp-text">稍后再找</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 最终彩蛋结果弹窗 -->
        <div id="final-result-modal" class="modal final-result-modal">
            <div class="final-result-content">
                <div class="final-result-badge" id="final-result-icon">🏆</div>
                <h3 id="final-result-title">工业探秘者</h3>
                <p id="final-result-text">可前往服务台揭晓答案。</p>
                <button class="stamp-btn small" id="final-result-close">
                    <span class="stamp-text">太棒了</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 小助手 -->
        <div id="assistant" class="assistant">
            <div class="assistant-bubble" id="assistant-bubble">
                <p id="assistant-text">你好呀，我是公元小灵！</p>
            </div>
            <button class="assistant-mute-btn" id="assistant-mute-btn" title="静音">🔊</button>
            <div class="assistant-avatar" id="assistant-avatar">
                <span class="avatar-face">🧙</span>
                <span class="avatar-ring"></span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 证书页 -->
        <div id="certificate-page" class="page">
            <div class="certificate-container" id="certificate-container">
                <div class="certificate-border">
                    <div class="certificate-inner">
                        <div class="cert-header">
                            <h2>荣誉证书</h2>
                            <div class="cert-subtitle">CERTIFICATE OF ACHIEVEMENT</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="cert-body">
                            <p class="cert-text">兹证明</p>
                            <p class="cert-name" id="cert-name">探秘者</p>
                            <p class="cert-text">
                                在汕头工业博物馆<br>
                                "公元感光工业探秘"活动中<br>
                                成功完成全部关卡挑战
                            </p>
                            <div class="cert-badges" id="cert-badges">
                                <span style="opacity:0.3;">🚶</span><span style="opacity:0.3;">💡</span><span style="opacity:0.3;">🥇</span><span style="opacity:0.3;">🏭</span><span style="opacity:0.3;">🧪</span><span style="opacity:0.3;">🧩</span><span style="opacity:0.3;">⚗️</span><span style="opacity:0.3;">⚡</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="cert-title">荣获<span class="highlight">"汕头工业探秘者"</span>称号</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="cert-footer">
                            <div class="cert-seal">
                                <div class="seal-text">汕头工业博物馆</div>
                                <div class="seal-date" id="cert-date">2026年7月</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="cert-souvenir">可保存本证书前往服务台领取实体纪念品一份！</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cert-actions">
                <button class="stamp-btn" id="save-cert-btn">
                    <span class="stamp-text">保存证书</span>
                </button>
                <button class="stamp-btn outline" id="back-to-game-btn">
                    <span class="stamp-text">返回游戏</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

